snippet.title: Animamundi - Dark Alchemist - Opening Movie
snippet.description:
This Opening Movie is from a Bishoujo Game called Animamundi - Dark Alchemist. It is published by Karin entertainment / VanillaSugarStudio / now defunct Hirameki International.

In memoriam to Hirameki International. May they live forever in our hearts.
